1. "*Ijudi* su stvoreni da budu dobri jedni prema drugima." (People are created to be good to each other.)

2. "On je sve što *ijudi* mogu da budu." (He is all that people can be.)

3. "Oni su najveća *ijudina* nada." (They are the greatest hope of people.)

4. "Misli o *ijudima* su pozitivne." (Thoughts about people are positive.)

5. "*Ijudi* moraju da se međusobno poštuju." (People must respect each other.)